      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection i had on my arm. i've been taking them for like 3 days now and the redness is totally gone and it doesn't even hurt anymore. i feel way better now. do i really need to keep taking them if the infection looks like it's already cleared up?",
