    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the resistance thing but i'm just really worried about putting more chemicals in my body if i don't actually need them anymore. if there's no redness and no pain, isn't that a sign the medicine has already done its job? it feels like a lot of unnecessary stuff to take for another week if the problem is gone.",
